description.en:
While working overtime through several nights, I fell asleep for a short while. When I woke up, I seemed to be possessing the villain of the webnovel I was reading.

&quot;Well, how typically clich&eacute;... to the point where I'd end up dead if I were to follow the predetermined fate. Darn it.&quot;

I need to find a way to survive.

The first way to survive as a good-for-nothing villain in the webnovel: &quot;Convince as many people as possible to be on my side.&quot;

The second way to survive as a good-for-nothing villain in the webnovel: &quot;Become strong enough to protect myself.&quot;

Lastly, the third way to survive as a good-for-nothing villain in the webnovel: &quot;Never become friendly with that proud and insane 'Summoned Master'.&quot;

But what should I do?
Even before I possessed this body, the original owner already caused an incident.

&quot;Use your money to kill the 'Summoned Master' who has yet to regain his power? Are you crazy? Then who will stop the Demon King?&quot;

This is the beginning of the modern-day survival + dungeon-raider fantasy story of Choi Yu-Seong, the possessed villain who wants to live a laid-back lifestyle!

&lt;This is the webtoon version of the author So Yu-Hyeon's popular webnovel, &quot;Trapped in a Webnovel as a Good-for-Nothing&quot;.&gt;

[u][b]Espa&ntilde;ol / Espa&ntilde;ol:[/b][/u]  [spoiler]
Luego de trabajar horas extras durante varias noches, me qued&eacute; dormido por un rato. Cuando me despert&eacute;, parec&iacute;a haber pose&iacute;do al villano de la novela web que estaba leyendo. &ldquo;Bien, qu&eacute; clich&eacute; tan t&iacute;pico&hellip; al punto en que terminar&iacute;a muerto si siguiera el destino predeterminado. Maldita sea.&rdquo; Necesito encontrar una manera de sobrevivir.
El primer modo de sobrevivir como un villano bueno para nada en la novela web: &ldquo;Convencer a tanta gente como sea posible de estar de mi lado.&rdquo;
El segundo modo de sobrevivir como un villano bueno para nada en la novela web: &ldquo;Volverme suficientemente fuerte para protegerme a m&iacute; mismo.&rdquo;
Finalmente, el tercer modo de sobrevivir como un villano bueno para nada en la novela web: &ldquo;Nunca volverse amigable con el orgulloso y demente 'Maestro Invocado'&rdquo;.
Pero &iquest;qu&eacute; deber&iacute;a hacer? Incluso antes de poseer este cuerpo, el due&ntilde;o original ya hab&iacute;a causado un incidente.
&ldquo;&iquest;Usar tu dinero para matar al 'Maestro Invocado' quien todav&iacute;a tiene que recobrar su poder? &iquest;Est&aacute;s loco? &iquest;Entonces qui&eacute;n va a detener al Rey Demonio?&rdquo;
&iexcl;Este es el comienzo de historia de la supervivencia en d&iacute;as modernos + fantas&iacute;a del asaltante de mazmorras Choi Yu-Seong, el villano pose&iacute;do que quiere vivir una vida despreocupada![/spoiler]
